description:
Hillary Clinton has accused Donald Trump of re-enacting a Nazi rally by holding an event in Madison Square Garden this weekend. It comes after Kamala Harris called him "a fascist". Desperate stuff.

The post Hillary Clinton Says Trump’s Madison Square Garden Event is a “Nazi Rally” appeared first on The Daily Sceptic.
title: Hillary Clinton Says Trump’s Madison Square Garden Event is a “Nazi Rally”

description:
A mother said her family was "lucky to have got out safely" after their parked electric car exploded and engulfed their house in flames.

The post “Why Did Our Parked Electric Car Explode?” appeared first on The Daily Sceptic.
title: “Why Did Our Parked Electric Car Explode?”

description:
In Germany, taxpayers are being charged billions of euros when the sun shines under contracts that commit the Government to paying solar energy producers the difference between a generous fixed tariff and the market rate.

The post The Country Where Taxpayers Are Charged Billions When the Sun Shines appeared first on The Daily Sceptic.
title: The Country Where Taxpayers Are Charged Billions When the Sun Shines

description:
Keir Starmer's much-hyped International Investment Summit claimed to secure £63bn, but nearly two thirds of this is not new and much of the rest is subsidised and will only lead to higher energy bills, says David Turver.

The post Starmer’s International Investment Summit Was a Sham appeared first on The Daily Sceptic.
title: Starmer’s International Investment Summit Was a Sham

description:
